high_descs: Go to the white refrigerator, turn right, and go to the far white counter.
Pick up the large knife from the white counter.
Turn around and go to the gray table.
Slice the lettuce on the gray table.
Turn to the left and turn to the right.
Put the knife on the gray table next to the gray bowl.
Turn to the right and turn to the left.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the gray table.
Turn around, turn to the right, and turn to the left to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the lettuce in the refrigerator, close the refrigerator, wait for three seconds, open the refrigerator, take out the lettuce, and close the refrigerator.
Turn to the left and go to the gray table.
Put the lettuce on the gray table.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of chilled lettuce on the table.

high_descs: move across the room to the refrigerator and turn right and all the way to the counter
pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the counter that is behind the plate
turn around and go across the room turning to the left to face the black table at the end of the kitchen
slice a piece of lettuce from the head of lettuce sitting on the table with the knife
move slightly left to face the bowl on the table
put the knife on the table to the right of the bowl
move slightly right to face the head of lettuce on the table
pick up the slice of lettuce from the table
turn around to face the front of the refrigerator
open the fridge doors and put the slice of lettuce on the top shelf, close the doors and open the doors again after five seconds and remove the lettuce slice
turn around to face the round black table
put the chilled slice of lettuce on the table next to the right of the remaining head of lettuce
anns.task_desc: put a slice of chilled lettuce on the table

high_descs: Walk toward the refrigerator, hang a right at the counter, walk to the knife and plate to the left of the microwave oven.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn around and walk with the knife to the table at the other end of the room, stand to the right of the chair while facing the table.
Slice the the head of lettuce nearest the gray bowl on the table into sections.
Turn slightly to your left and stand in front of the gray bowl.
Put the knife down to the right of the bowl.
Step back to the sliced head of lettuce.
Pick up the end slice of the lettuce closest to you.
Turn and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and place the lettuce slice on the top shelf of the fridge. After cooling, open the refrigerator door and pick up the lettuce slice and close the fridge door.
Turn and walk back to the table and go to the sliced head of lettuce.
Place the chilled slice next to the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Slice a head of lettuce into sections, chill one slice, return it to the table

high_descs: Walk few steps then turn right head to the counter beside the microwave
Pick up the knife beside the plate on the counter
Turn around to your right and head to the table
Slice the cabbage beside the fork on the table
Turn to your left, make a step, turn to your right
Drop the knife beside the sliced cabbage and the bowl on the table
Turn to your right then make a step then turn to your left facing the table
Pick up one slice of cabbage on the table
Turn to your left then walk towards the fridge
Open the fridge put in the cabbage then close fridge, open and get the cabbage then close it again
Turn to your left walk towards the table
Put back the slice of cabbage on the same place where you get it
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of cabbage on the fridge going back to the table

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room and face the left side of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn left to face the right side of the kitchen table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Step to the left and face the table.
Place the knife down on the table.
Take a step to the right and face the lettuce on the table.
pick up a slice of the lettuce on the table.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cool the slice of lettuce in the fridge and remove it.
TUrn around to face the lettuce on the table.
Place the lettuce slice on the table with the rest of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: To cut plus cool a slice of lettuce as well as return it to the table.
